{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "smartdtc-api-collection-v1",
    "name": "SmartDTC API",
    "description": "Complete API reference for the SmartDTC AI-Driven Bus Scheduling & Management System.\n\n**Base URL** (Backend): `{{baseUrl}}`  \n**AI Service URL**: `{{aiUrl}}`\n\n## Quick Start\n1. Run `POST Auth/Login` — the token is saved automatically to `{{token}}`\n2. All protected endpoints read from `{{token}}` via the collection-level auth header\n\n## Roles\n- `passenger` — read-only tracking + rating\n- `driver` — active trip management\n- `dispatcher` — schedule + demand management\n- `admin` — full access including reports, driver/bus assignment, AI retrain",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:5000/api/v1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "aiUrl",   "value": "http://localhost:8000",         "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token",   "value": "",                               "type": "string" },
    { "key": "routeId", "value": "64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1",     "type": "string" },
    { "key": "busId",   "value": "64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d2",     "type": "string" },
    { "key": "driverId","value": "64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d3",     "type": "string" },
    { "key": "scheduleId","value": "64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d4",   "type": "string" },
    { "key": "tripId",  "value": "64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d5",     "type": "string" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "User authentication and token management.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth","register"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Test Admin\",\n  \"email\": \"admin@smartdtc.in\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin@1234\",\n  \"role\": \"admin\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token); }",
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Token present', () => pm.expect(json.token).to.be.a('string'));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth","login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@smartdtc.in\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin@1234\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/me", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth","me"] }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth","refresh"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{ \"refreshToken\": \"<your_refresh_token>\" }"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/logout", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth","logout"] }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Routes",
